FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
Increase from FY26 values (under PE 0605414N) to FY27 is due to continued software development required
to deliver the MQ-25A capability directly to the fleet. This includes the continued development and integration
of essential software, such as Relative Navigation (RELNAV), which enables the MQ-25A to reliably recover
on a CVN. Furthermore, the increased funding supports the expansion of Technical Data Package (TDP)
development for shipboard systems and begins to address the obsolescence of test assets, ensuring the
program remains on track for its Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) phase and successful fleet
deployment.
