D. Acquisition Strategy
This is a non-ACAT program. Project includes analysis to support development of IMD requirements and integration documents to deliver M&S tool, data and associated
environments focused on integration, interoperability, prioritization and trades on threat data/modeling of intelligence data being fielded. Project efforts will support
various afloat and ashore Navy programs and systems to assess intelligence data impact on complex mission performance and conduct trades on threat data/modeling
prioritization to supporting reprogramming, engineering and test environments.




