The increase of +$0.107 million from FY 2026 to FY 2027 reflects the ramp-up of planned activities, including the fielding
of Classified Retransmission Devices (RDs), expansion of Zero Trust integration across unclassified and classified mobility
environments, enhancement of Mobile DLP/DRM, and the continued development of cross-domain and 5G mobility capabilities to
meet growing operational requirements.
