Description: UCME supports the transition of maritime focused Science and Technology (S&T) efforts and
provides a rapid response capability to support SOF underwater craft and diver systems, subsystems, and
their emerging requirements. UCME provides technology refresh efforts to correct system deficiencies, improve
asset life, and enhance mission capability to leverage and exploit emerging technologies within the maritime
SOF undersea capability portfolio. UCME focuses on spearheading specific Technology Readiness Level
(TRL) 6 technology for compatibility, maturity, marinization, and successful transition to the SOF undersea craft
programs.

