Title: Small Unmanned Surface Vehicle (SUSV), Program Number V36                                                        1.920       0.000       1.990           -       1.990
Description: The SOF SUSV program procures COTS modular systems that house government-off-the-shelf
(GOTS) payloads in accordance with Special Operations Rapid Requirements Document (SORRD). The SUSV
fielding is divided into two endurance categories to address missions lasting a few days (short endurance (SE))
and missions lasting from months to years (long endurance (LE)). Together SE and LE address contested
logistics, enables access to contested / denied areas in the maritime domain, and reduces risk to personnel
and manned platforms. The SE platforms will provide maritime special reconnaissance capabilities while LE
platforms will provide persistent maritime ISR.

FY 2026 Plans:
Finalize SE integration work in to support Operational Test. Begin LE USV modular payload integration and
authority to operate compliance.

